title: Grateful Dead Live at Ventura County Fairgrounds on 1987-06-13
description:
Set 1

Mississippi Half Step-> Walkin' Blues, Row Jimmy, When I Paint My Masterpiece*, When Push Comes To Shove, Cassidy, Friend Of The Devil, Let It Grow

Set 2

Shakedown Street, Saint Of Circumstance, Ship of Fools, Estimated Prophet-> Eyes Of The World-> Drums-> Space-> The Other One-> Morning Dew-> Sugar Magnolia, E: Black Muddy River

* First time played
